{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":396,"text":"What is love?"},{"time":3654,"text":"It's a hard term to define"},{"time":5961,"text":"in so far as it has a very wide application."},{"time":9850,"text":"I can love jogging."},{"time":11619,"text":"I can love a book, a movie."},{"time":13645,"text":"I can love escalopes."},{"time":16516,"text":"I can love my wife."},{"time":18711,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":23776,"text":"But there's a great difference"},{"time":26810,"text":"between an escalope and my wife, for instance."},{"time":31901,"text":"That is, if I value the escalope,"},{"time":34906,"text":"the escalope, on the other hand, \nit doesn't value me back."},{"time":41019,"text":"Whereas my wife, she calls me"},{"time":44321,"text":"the star of her life."},{"time":46122,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":48706,"text":"Therefore, only another desiring conscience"},{"time":50662,"text":"can conceive me as a desirable being."},{"time":53894,"text":"I know this, that's why"},{"time":55474,"text":"love can be defined in a more accurate way"},{"time":57820,"text":"as the desire of being desired."},{"time":62130,"text":"Hence the eternal problem of love:"},{"time":64925,"text":"how to become and remain desirable?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":70869,"text":"The individual used to find"},{"time":74489,"text":"an answer to this problem"},{"time":76722,"text":"by submitting his life to community rules."},{"time":79727,"text":"You had a specific part to play"},{"time":81834,"text":"according to your sex, your age,"},{"time":84049,"text":"your social status,"},{"time":85925,"text":"and you only had to play your part"},{"time":87955,"text":"to be valued and loved by the whole community."},{"time":92032,"text":"Think about the young woman\nwho must remain chaste before marriage."},{"time":95789,"text":"Think about the youngest son \nwho must obey the eldest son,"},{"time":100155,"text":"who in turn must obey the patriarch."}]},{"cues":[{"time":105861,"text":"But a phenomenon"},{"time":110147,"text":"started in the 13th century,"},{"time":113510,"text":"mainly in the Renaissance, in the West,"},{"time":117512,"text":"that caused the biggest identity crisis"},{"time":120891,"text":"in the history of humankind."},{"time":123088,"text":"This phenomenon is modernity."},{"time":125358,"text":"We can basically summarize it\nthrough a triple process."},{"time":128306,"text":"First, a process of rationalization\nof scientific research,"},{"time":134029,"text":"which has accelerated technical progress."},{"time":136714,"text":"Next, a process of political democratization,"},{"time":141178,"text":"which has fostered individual rights."},{"time":144292,"text":"And finally, a process of rationalization \nof economic production"},{"time":148850,"text":"and of trade liberalization."}]},{"cues":[{"time":151735,"text":"These three intertwined processes"},{"time":154617,"text":"have completely annihilated"},{"time":157026,"text":"all the traditional bearings of Western societies,"},{"time":161332,"text":"with radical consequences for the individual."},{"time":163957,"text":"Now individuals are free"},{"time":166518,"text":"to value or disvalue"},{"time":169922,"text":"any attitude, any choice, any object."},{"time":174127,"text":"But as a result, they are themselves confronted"},{"time":180344,"text":"with this same freedom that others have"},{"time":182409,"text":"to value or disvalue them."},{"time":186861,"text":"In other words, my value was once ensured"},{"time":192201,"text":"by submitting myself \nto the traditional authorities."},{"time":196114,"text":"Now it is quoted in the stock exchange."}]},{"cues":[{"time":201398,"text":"On the free market of individual desires,"},{"time":206048,"text":"I negotiate my value every day."},{"time":210033,"text":"Hence the anxiety of contemporary man."},{"time":212619,"text":"He is obsessed: \"Am I desirable? How desirable?"},{"time":216705,"text":"How many people are going to love me?\""},{"time":219803,"text":"And how does he respond to this anxiety?"},{"time":222509,"text":"Well, by hysterically collecting\nsymbols of desirability."},{"time":232493,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":235460,"text":"I call this act of collecting,"},{"time":237765,"text":"along with others, seduction capital."},{"time":241119,"text":"Indeed, our consumer society"},{"time":243162,"text":"is largely based on seduction capital."},{"time":248631,"text":"It is said about this consumption\nthat our age is materialistic."},{"time":252742,"text":"But it's not true! We only accumulate objects"},{"time":256690,"text":"in order to communicate with other minds."},{"time":259501,"text":"We do it to make them love us, to seduce them."},{"time":264918,"text":"Nothing could be less materialistic, \nor more sentimental,"},{"time":268638,"text":"than a teenager buying brand new jeans"},{"time":272863,"text":"and tearing them at the knees,"},{"time":275355,"text":"because he wants to please Jennifer."},{"time":277467,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":279917,"text":"Consumerism is not materialism."},{"time":283201,"text":"It is rather what is swallowed up"},{"time":285276,"text":"and sacrificed in the name of the god of love,"},{"time":288285,"text":"or rather in the name of seduction capital."}]},{"cues":[{"time":292731,"text":"In light of this observation on contemporary love,"},{"time":298112,"text":"how can we think of love in the years to come?"},{"time":301427,"text":"We can envision two hypotheses:"},{"time":303711,"text":"The first one consists of betting"},{"time":306447,"text":"that this process of narcissistic \ncapitalization will intensify."},{"time":312141,"text":"It is hard to say what shape \nthis intensification will take,"},{"time":316209,"text":"because it largely depends"},{"time":317940,"text":"on social and technical innovations,"},{"time":320708,"text":"which are by definition difficult to predict."},{"time":325755,"text":"But we can, for instance,"},{"time":327657,"text":"imagine a dating website"},{"time":331381,"text":"which, a bit like those loyalty points programs,"},{"time":335513,"text":"uses seduction capital points"},{"time":338705,"text":"that vary according to my age, \nmy height/weight ratio,"},{"time":342500,"text":"my degree, my salary,"},{"time":345023,"text":"or the number of clicks on my profile."},{"time":349488,"text":"We can also imagine"},{"time":353374,"text":"a chemical treatment for breakups"},{"time":356747,"text":"that weakens the feelings of attachment."}]},{"cues":[{"time":360565,"text":"By the way, there's a program on MTV already"},{"time":364622,"text":"in which seduction teachers"},{"time":368606,"text":"treat heartache as a disease."},{"time":372524,"text":"These teachers call themselves \"pick-up artists.\""},{"time":376226,"text":"\"Artist\" in French is easy, it means \"artiste.\""},{"time":379470,"text":"\"Pick-up\" is to pick someone up,"},{"time":382182,"text":"but not just any picking up -- it's picking up chicks."},{"time":384298,"text":"So they are artists of picking up chicks."},{"time":388767,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":390224,"text":"And they call heartache \"one-itis.\""},{"time":395339,"text":"In English, \"itis\" is a suffix that signifies infection."},{"time":398889,"text":"One-itis can be translated as \"an infection from one.\""},{"time":403353,"text":"It's a bit disgusting. Indeed, for the pick-up artists,"},{"time":407122,"text":"falling in love with someone"},{"time":410571,"text":"is a waste of time,"},{"time":412403,"text":"it's squandering your seduction capital,"},{"time":414310,"text":"so it must be eliminated"},{"time":416102,"text":"like a disease, like an infection."},{"time":419831,"text":"We can also envision"},{"time":423532,"text":"a romantic use of the genome."},{"time":426549,"text":"Everyone would carry it around"},{"time":430199,"text":"and present it like a business card"},{"time":433399,"text":"to verify if seduction can progress to reproduction."},{"time":438393,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":442021,"text":"Of course, this race for seduction,"},{"time":447184,"text":"like every fierce competition,"},{"time":449287,"text":"will create huge disparities \nin narcissistic satisfaction,"},{"time":454220,"text":"and therefore a lot of loneliness and frustration too."},{"time":458270,"text":"So we can expect that modernity itself,"},{"time":461014,"text":"which is the origin of seduction capital,\nwould be called into question."},{"time":465550,"text":"I'm thinking particularly of the reaction"},{"time":468181,"text":"of neo-fascist or religious communes."},{"time":473110,"text":"But such a future doesn't have to be."}]},{"cues":[{"time":478746,"text":"Another path to thinking about love may be possible."},{"time":484168,"text":"But how?"},{"time":486258,"text":"How to renounce the hysterical need to be valued?"},{"time":490572,"text":"Well, by becoming aware\nof my uselessness."},{"time":494780,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":496879,"text":"Yes,"},{"time":497818,"text":"I'm useless."},{"time":500109,"text":"But rest assured:"},{"time":501980,"text":"so are you."},{"time":503442,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":505592,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":509629,"text":"We are all useless."},{"time":513999,"text":"This uselessness is easily demonstrated,"},{"time":516414,"text":"because in order to be valued"},{"time":520015,"text":"I need another to desire me,"},{"time":523026,"text":"which shows that I do not have any value of my own."},{"time":525316,"text":"I don't have any inherent value."},{"time":530764,"text":"We all pretend to have an idol;"},{"time":533489,"text":"we all pretend to be an idol for\nsomeone else, but actually"},{"time":536408,"text":"we are all impostors, a bit like a man on the street"},{"time":539830,"text":"who appears totally cool and indifferent,"},{"time":542689,"text":"while he has actually anticipated and calculated"},{"time":545838,"text":"so that all eyes are on him."}]},{"cues":[{"time":549443,"text":"I think that becoming aware"},{"time":551012,"text":"of this general imposture"},{"time":553219,"text":"that concerns all of us"},{"time":554627,"text":"would ease our love relationships."},{"time":556447,"text":"It is because I want to be loved"},{"time":558837,"text":"from head to toe,"},{"time":560334,"text":"justified in my every choice,"},{"time":562309,"text":"that the seduction hysteria exists."},{"time":565081,"text":"And therefore I want to seem perfect"},{"time":567374,"text":"so that another can love me."},{"time":568994,"text":"I want them to be perfect"},{"time":570521,"text":"so that I can be reassured of my value."},{"time":572678,"text":"It leads to couples"},{"time":575065,"text":"obsessed with performance"},{"time":577357,"text":"who will break up, just like that,"},{"time":579513,"text":"at the slightest underachievement."}]},{"cues":[{"time":582067,"text":"In contrast to this attitude,"},{"time":586190,"text":"I call upon tenderness -- love as tenderness."},{"time":588928,"text":"What is tenderness?"},{"time":590296,"text":"To be tender is to accept \nthe loved one's weaknesses."},{"time":594169,"text":"It's not about becoming a sad couple of orderlies."},{"time":597826,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":599021,"text":"That's pretty bad."},{"time":601091,"text":"On the contrary,"},{"time":602423,"text":"there's plenty of charm and happiness in tenderness."},{"time":605189,"text":"I refer specifically to a kind of humor\nthat is unfortunately underused."},{"time":609238,"text":"It is a sort of poetry of deliberate awkwardness."}]},{"cues":[{"time":612115,"text":"I refer to self-mockery."},{"time":614896,"text":"For a couple who is no longer sustained, supported"},{"time":617717,"text":"by the constraints of tradition,"},{"time":619794,"text":"I believe that self-mockery"},{"time":621342,"text":"is one of the best means for \nthe relationship to endure."}]}]}